These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, puzzles, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | juice   |
| Hobby      | woodworking    | puzzles  | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, rose, balloon-flower
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian
1. the argentine is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the canadian is the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Flower      | rose | amaryllis     | balloon-flower      |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, water
3 different games are played: scrabble, chess, snooker
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water  | tea       |
| Game       | scrabble     | chess | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, d&b, salsa
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, woodworking
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre    | salsa    | d&b     | funk |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | puzzles     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hedgehog
3 different games are played: snooker, billiard, bridge
1. the person playing billiard is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | bird     | hedgehog |
| Game   | bridge        | snooker | billiard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, house, blues
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the fan of house is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the fan of blues is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre        | blues | hip-hop      | house  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
