3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the tower house##1
2. the wooden house is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| House   | gothic-revival      | tower     | wooden    |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish | ferret |

