.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, water-polo
3 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Sport   | water-polo | golf | biathlon  |
| Pet     | rat     | horse      | rabbit |

