.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, tea
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, may, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | cola   | sprite    | tea    |
| Birthday   | may | december | march |

