2. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| City   | colone    | miami     | marseilles   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | brazilian | nigerian |

