.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, radish, zucchini
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, trike, skateboard
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating zucchini is in the middle##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | asparagus     | zucchini   | radish     |
| Transport    | skateboard | trike | subway |

