.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, spy, adventure
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, pop
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Movie-Genre      | time-travel  | adventure | spy  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | pop   | classical |

