There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, ivory, pink
1. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
2. the person eating garlic is the person who likes pink##1
3. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | nectarine | papaya   | garlic        |
| Color   | ivory    | emerald | pink |

