.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, pepper, spinach
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, chestnut, lavender
1. the person who likes chestnut is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | spinach | cherry       | pepper  |
| Color   | lavender  | chestnut | ivory |

 